      "review_summary": "The PR adds fallback-run metadata, completion-announcement provenance detection, announcement prompt hardening, and an embedded `sessions_spawn` guard with focused tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +86, Tests +142. Total +228 across 18 files.\n\nReproducibility: Partly: the linked production incident and source paths show a credible fallback-completion path with native spawning still available, but I did not run a controlled current-main end-to-end fallback reproduction.",
